\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {I}{\ignorespaces The mechanism against the record. Six established facts about {Na$_x$CoO$_2\cdot y$H$_2$O} and what the soft-mode, charge-bifurcation picture makes of each: five are explained by the static calculation, and one---the superconductivity of the bilayer hydrate at $9.9$~\r A---is a prediction contingent on water re-softening the sodium well (Sec.~\ref {sec:difficulty}). The one-line reason for each verdict is given.}}{11}{}}
